T1  - An optimized ERP brain–computer interface based on facial expression changes
A1  - Jing Jin and Ian Daly and Yu Zhang and Xingyu Wang and Andrzej Cichocki
Y1  - 2014
SP  - 036004
JF  - Journal of Neural Engineering
VL  - 11
IS  - 3
