T1  - Hidden Markov model and support vector machine based decoding of finger movements using
electrocorticography
A1  - Tobias Wissel and Tim Pfeiffer and Robert Frysch and Robert T Knight and Edward F Chang and Hermann Hinrichs and Jochem W
Rieger and Georg Rose
Y1  - 2013
SP  - 056020
JF  - Journal of Neural Engineering
