A1  - Sidath Ravindra Liyanage and Cuntai Guan and Haihong Zhang and Kai Keng Ang and JianXin Xu and Tong Heng Lee
Y1  - 2013
SP  - 036007
JF  - Journal of Neural Engineering
VL  - 10
