T1  - Estimating workload using EEG spectral power and ERPs in the n-back task
A1  - Anne-Marie Brouwer and Maarten A Hogervorst and Jan B F van Erp and Tobias Heffelaar and Patrick H Zimmerman and Robert
Oostenveld
Y1  - 2012
SP  - 045008
JF  - Journal of Neural Engineering
