T1  - Flashing characters with famous faces improves ERP-based brain–computer interface performance
A1  - T Kaufmann and S M Schulz and C Grünzinger and A Kübler
Y1  - 2011
SP  - 056016
JF  - Journal of Neural Engineering
VL  - 8
